Package: CommonFunctions
Type: Package
Title: Commonly used functions related to the marketing panel data, especially the
  data that has been aggregated at the brand level.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: George Gui
Maintainer: George Gui <guizhida@gmail.com>
Description:  This package provides convenient utility function for marketing
  research based on the a marketing panel data. It includes a set of loading,
  formatting, and graphing functions.
